snippet.title: A Wake Inn | VR | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch Teaser of upcoming immersive VR horror game, which will change your view on exploration experiences forever.

Add us to your wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1383690/A_Wake_Inn/

Subscribe the newsletter and don't miss any juicy update:
http://www.awakeinngame.com/signup.html

Ask us anything on our official Subreddit:
https://www.reddit.com/r/AWakeInn/comments/hs6nug/rawakeinn_lounge/

or on our Discord channel: 
https://discord.gg/9vZdfVG

Follow us on social media:
https://www.facebook.com/awakeinn
https://twitter.com/awakeinngame
https://www.instagram.com/a_wake_inn/

Used song "Omen" thanks to courtesy of electro duo William Blake X Pan Listopad
